title: AGO, Accredited Renewable Energy Sites, Australia, 2008
name: AGO, Accredited Renewable Energy Sites, Australia, 2008
description: The accredited renewables webmap contains locations of Australian accredited renewable power stations that are greater than 3kW. Each power station has such information as fuel type, technology used, size (kW), ownership, latitude and longitude and data source. Web links and site photographs are provided where possible. A download feature is provided for clients who want the base data.
